{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "tiles-ecommerce-api-collection",
		"name": "Tiles E-Commerce API - Complete Collection",
		"description": "Complete API collection for testing Tiles E-Commerce Backend\n\n**Base URL:** http://localhost:4000\n\n**How to use:**\n1. Start backend server: `cd backend && npm start`\n2. Import this collection in Postman\n3. Test APIs in this order:\n   - Register User\n   - Login User (saves token automatically)\n   - Test other APIs\n\n**Note:** Some APIs require authentication. Login first to get JWT token.",
